STEP 1 :
    Establishing a connection:     mongoose.connect(<URL STRING>)
STEP 2:
    Creating a Schema:     const ItemSchema = { name: String}
STEP 3:
    Creating Model:   const Item(should start with capital letter) = mongoose.model("Item"(should be sigular form), ItemSchema) 
STEP 4:
    Creating Item : const item1 = new Item({ name: "Adding new Item"})
Step 5: 
    Adding New Item: Item.insertOne(item1).then(()=>{console.log("item inserted Successfully")}).catch((err)=>{console.log(err));
    
